  "pages": [
    {
      "page": 1,
      "title": "Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<p>The Affordable Connectivity Program (ACP) offers $30 discounts on cell phone and internet bills, alongside the Lifeline free government cell phone program. With both, you can enjoy unlimited talk, texts, and internet for free. The discounts are accessible in 50 states, DC, and Puerto Rico. Here are details about ACP.</p>\n<img alt=\"Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet_1\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_1.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_1.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_1.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_1.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 2,
      "title": "Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>1. What Is ACP</h4>\n<img alt=\"Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet_2\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_2.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_2.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_2.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_2.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>The Emergency Broadband Benefit (EBB) program, a short-term initiative, concluded on March 1, 2022. However, it will swiftly transition into the Affordable Connectivity Program (ACP), a permanent program that boasts substantial federal funding amounting to $14.2 billion. </p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 3,
      "title": "Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>2. Household Benefits</h4>\n<img alt=\"Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet_3\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_3.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_3.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_3.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_3.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>The ACP benefit grants eligible households a monthly discount of up to $30 for internet service. On qualifying Tribal lands, qualifying households can receive even greater discounts, up to $75 per month.</p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 4,
      "title": "Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>3. Added Bonus</h4>\n<img alt=\"Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet_4\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_4.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_4.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_4.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_4.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>As stated by the Federal Communications Commission, eligible households can also avail a singular rebate worth a maximum of $100 to acquire a laptop, desktop computer, or tablet from designated providers. However, in order to qualify for this assistance, households must contribute an amount exceeding $10 but lower than $50 towards the total purchase price. </p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 5,
      "title": "Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>4. Requirements Of ACP</h4>\n<img alt=\"Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet_5\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_5.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_5.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_5.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_5.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>According to the FCC, your family can qualify if: </p>\n<p>1) Income is at or below 200% of the federal poverty guidelines </p>\n<p>2) Participate in certain assistance programs like SNAP, Medicaid, Public Housing Assistance, SSI, WIC, or Lifeline </p>\n<p>3) Participate in Tribal programs like Bureau of Indian Affairs General Assistance, Tribal TANF, or Food Distribution Program on Indian Reservations </p>\n<p>4) Approved for free or reduced-price school lunches or breakfasts </p>\n<p>5) Receive a Federal Pell Grant </p>\n<p>6) Meet eligibility criteria for a low-income program by a participating provider. </p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 6,
      "title": "Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>5. Restrictions Of ACP</h4>\n<img alt=\"Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet_6\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_6.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_6.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_6.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_6.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>Similar to the Lifeline government cell phone program, the ACP also restricts one monthly service discount and device discount per household. However, these programs are independent. Thus, you can be eligible for both simultaneously. </p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 7,
      "title": "Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet",
      "article": "<div class=\"article\">\n<h1>Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet</h1>\n<div class=\"ads ads-detail-one\" id=\"ads1\">\n<div class=\"advertisement\">Advertisement</div>\n<script async=\"\" crossorigin=\"anonymous\" src=\"https://pagead2.googlesyndication.com/pagead/js/adsbygoogle.js?client=ca-pub-2972155632292532\"></script>\n<!-- Phone Ads 1 -->\n<ins class=\"adsbygoogle\" data-ad-client=\"ca-pub-2972155632292532\" data-ad-format=\"auto\" data-ad-slot=\"2576564749\" data-full-width-responsive=\"true\" style=\"display:block\"></ins>\n<script>\n     (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});\n</script>\n</div>\n<h4>6. Annual Recertification</h4>\n<img alt=\"Affordable Connectivity Program Pays For Your Phone And Internet_7\" class=\"old_img\" data-smallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_7.jpg\" data-src=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_7.jpg\" data-webpsmallsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content_small/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_7.webp\" data-webpsrc=\"//cdn.uslowcosthousing.com/Images/content/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet/affordable-connectivity-program-pays-for-your-phone-and-internet_7.webp\" lazyload=\"\" src=\"/Public/Images/load.png\">\n<p>You will need to undergo an annual recertification process to confirm your eligibility for continued receipt of ACP benefits. This process is similar to the mandatory verification procedure for receiving Lifeline Free Government Cell Phone benefits. </p>\n</img></div>"
    },
    {
      "page": 8,
